ANC youths yesterday praised their leader Musalia Mudavadi as a great leader who has the interests of the youth at heart .Nairobi youth leader Esemele Amugune said Mudavadi will help the youth and people living with disabilities succeed if elected President.He spoke at a Nairobi hotel, where he was accompanied by youths from the 47 counties. He s the best person to address historical injustices and help the marginalised. Mudavadi s track record exemplifies transparency and accountability in his service to Kenyans, Esemele said.